               </header>

           
                                  
            
      <div id="wikiArticle" class="page-content boxed">
                <div id="article-nav">
          <div class="page-toc">
            <h2>Table of Contents</h2>
            <ol>
              <li><a href="Using_CSS_animations#Configuring_the_animation" rel="internal">Configuring the animation</a><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code><li><a href="Using_CSS_animations#Defining_the_animation_sequence_using_keyframes" rel="internal">Defining the animation sequence using keyframes</a><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code><li><a href="Using_CSS_animations#Examples" rel="internal">Examples</a><code></code><code></code><ol><li><a href="Using_CSS_animations#Making_text_slide_across_the_browser_window" rel="internal">Making text slide across the browser window</a><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code><ol><li><a href="Using_CSS_animations#Adding_another_keyframe" rel="internal">Adding another keyframe</a><li><a href="Using_CSS_animations#Making_it_repeat" rel="internal">Making it repeat</a><code></code><code></code><li><a href="Using_CSS_animations#Making_it_move_back_and_forth" rel="internal">Making it move back and forth</a><code></code><code></code></ol></li><li><a href="Using_CSS_animations#Using_animation_events" rel="internal">Using animation events</a><code></code><ol><li><a href="Using_CSS_animations#Adding_the_animation_event_listeners" rel="internal">Adding the animation event listeners</a><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code><li><a href="Using_CSS_animations#Receiving_the_events" rel="internal">Receiving the events</a><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code><li><a href="Using_CSS_animations#The_HTML" rel="internal">The HTML</a></ol></li></ol></li><li><a href="Using_CSS_animations#See_also" rel="internal">See also</a><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code><code></code>
            </ol>
          </div>
          <ul class="page-anchors">
            <li class="anchor-tags">
                              <i class="icon-tags"></i><a href="Using_CSS_animations#document-tags">Tags</a>
